  ('dietitian-moex-00765', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '營養照護程序（NutritionCareProcess）中，那一個階段是為治療營養問題採取的行動？', '["Nutritionscreen", "Nutritiondiagnosis", "Nutritionevaluation", "Nutritionintervention"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "45b10eeb9df5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e6f1e0f87add", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00766', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關衛教病人的營養諮詢策略及方法，下列何者正確？', '["CBT（cognitive behavioral therapy）是指計算行為理論，可以從此理論計算出病人吃了多少食 物是否與行為有關", "SCT（socialcognitivetheory）是指社會地位理論，可以了解病人所吃的食物內容與社會地位有關", "ACT（acceptanceandcommitmenttherapy）是指接納與承諾療法，主要是可以幫助病人澄清價 值觀，並採取適當的行動", "TTM（transtheoreticalmodel）是指病人經測試後進行策略改變，此模式的改變是單一的、不變的"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "45b10eeb9df5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e6f1e0f87add", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00767', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在營養照護程序中，執行NutritionIntervention時應包含的2個步驟，下列何者正確？', '["PlanningandImplementation", "Screeninganddocumentation", "Determiningetiologyandstatingsigns", "Collectingandanalyzingdata"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "45b10eeb9df5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e6f1e0f87add", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00768', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關治療飲食（therapeuticdiets）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["治療飲食以一般的、充足的飲食為基礎", "治療飲食不須考慮個人的社會心理因素", "治療飲食可以緩解或停止疾病的進展過程", "治療飲食會考慮個人的消化和吸收能力改變飲食的質與量達到滿足個人飲食需求"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "45b10eeb9df5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e6f1e0f87add", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
