  ('dietitian-moex-00770', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關腸道營養支持路徑的選擇取決條件，下列何者錯誤？', '["病人是否臥床", "是否計劃未來進行手術", "需要腸道營養支持的時間長度", "吸入性肺炎或餵食管移位的風險程度"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "45b10eeb9df5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e6f1e0f87add", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00771', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關泥狀食物胃造口飲食（PureedbyGastrostomyTubeDiet）目的，下列何者最不適當？', '["達到營養和水分的需求", "較適用於餵食幫浦（feedingpump）", "改善體重增加、生長和整體營養狀況", "改善和維持個人及其家庭的生活品質"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "45b10eeb9df5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e6f1e0f87add", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00772', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關hormones如何調控食慾和體重的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["Cholecystokinin由小腸細胞分泌，具促進食慾的作用", "Ghrelin由脂肪細胞分泌，可抑制食慾，纖瘦者濃度通常高於肥胖者", "Adiponectin 由脂肪細胞分泌，與體脂肪呈現正相關", "Leptin由脂肪細胞分泌，女性的濃度通常顯著高於男性"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "45b10eeb9df5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e6f1e0f87add", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
